  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `SprkChatAgentFactory.cs` + `PlaybookChatContextProvider.cs` to locate current per-turn assembly seam.</step>
    <step order="2">Read `PromptBudgetTracker.cs` for budget-enforcement API.</step>
    <step order="3">Implement (or refactor existing) static-prefix composition:
      - Compose blocks in the architecture-specified order
      - Use `LayeredContextCardBuilder` for the file-cards block (assert recently-discussed flag stripped — placed in dynamic suffix)
      - Use `TrustFrameInstructionInjector` for the trust-frame block
      - Validate total ≤6K tokens via `PromptBudgetTracker`
      - Log sessionId + totalPrefixTokens (tier-1 safe)</step>
    <step order="4">Implement byte-stability test: same session context (no file changes) → same prefix output byte-for-byte across N invocations.</step>
    <step order="5">Document open-question §12.1.1 resolution in code comment + notes/handoffs/079-recently-discussed-placement.md.</step>
    <step order="6">Run `dotnet build` + existing tests.</step>
